xdi2.messaging.container.interceptor.impl.encryption

Interface LiteralCryptoService

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractLiteralCryptoService, StaticLiteralCryptoService

    public interface LiteralCryptoService
    The purpose of this interface is to provide functionality for encrypting and decrypting literals in string form. This is used by the LiteralEncryptionInterceptor.
